  "page": "Fingers (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b><a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a></b> are narrow peninsulas of the northeastern Vale of Arryn. It may also refer to:\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fingers_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bethany_Fair-Fingers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bethany Fair-Fingers\">Bethany Fair-Fingers</a>, a singer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fingers_(ironman)\" title=\"Fingers (ironman)\">Fingers</a>, an ironborn.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hobb\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hobb\">Hobb</a>, known as \"Three-Finger Hobb\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nine-Finger_Jack\" title=\"Nine-Finger Jack\">Nine-Finger Jack</a>, a legendary hero from the riverlands.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a>, known as \"Littlefinger\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quickfinger\" title=\"Quickfinger\">Quickfinger</a>, a thief.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Toefinger\" title=\"Toefinger\">Toefinger</a>, a wildling raider.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Others\">Others</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fingers_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Others\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>\"<a href=\"/index.php/Fiery_fingers\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fiery fingers\">Fiery fingers</a>\", a nickname for men of the Fiery Hand.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fingers_(guards)\" title=\"Fingers (guards)\">Fingers</a>, personal guards to Lord Unwin Peake.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Flint%27s_Finger\" title=\"Flint&#39;s Finger\">Flint's Finger</a>, the seat of a branch of House Flint.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harpy%27s_fingers\" title=\"Harpy&#39;s fingers\">Harpy's fingers</a>, a whip.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Vale,_the_Fingers,_and_the_Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"High King of the Vale, the Fingers, and the Mountains of the Moon\">High King of the Vale, the Fingers, and the Mountains of the Moon</a>, a defunct title.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Fingers\" title=\"King of the Fingers\">King of the Fingers</a>, a defunct title.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Five_Fingers\" title=\"Lord of the Five Fingers\">Lord of the Five Fingers</a>, a defunct title.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fingers_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ben_Blackthumb\" title=\"Ben Blackthumb\">Ben Blackthumb</a>, a blacksmith.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Thumbs\" title=\"Stone Thumbs\">Stone Thumbs</a>, a wildling raider.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tessario\" title=\"Tessario\">Tessario</a>, known as \"Tessario the Thumb\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rule_of_thumb\" title=\"Rule of thumb\">Rule of thumb</a>, a law.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405160607\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.005 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 11/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16/1000000\nPost‐e